        "orgUnit": "/Employees",
        "mainText": "<p>I am an engineer at heart who is passionate about software as my craftsmanship - viewing clean code and architecture as an art.</p><p>I humbly accept that I can never know everything, but still choose to have it as my dream. I love to ask questions, learn, teach, and when needed - speak up.</p><p>My personal projects often include embedded programming and automation, but curiosity has taken me to other places as well.</p> ",
