        "orgUnit": "/Employees",
        "mainText": "<p>I’m Anna, a creative-minded explorer with a love for new technologies and design. With a background as an entrepreneur within design, crafts, and service, I strive to constantly grow while solving problems that matter and creating engaging solutions for products that people love!</p><p>One year ago I decided to start a new career and signed up for a Front End Bootcamp, the most fun thing I’ve tried in years.I stay motivated by learning new things, meeting new people, collaborating, and sharing my knowledge with others.</p><p>This has taken me from one craftsmanship to another. From being a hairdresser to become a goldsmith and now I believe I found my true spot as a developer, where my curiosity will never be fulfilled and my need for problem-solving will keep me moving forward.</p>                                                                                                                                                                    ",
