        "orgUnit": "/Employees",
        "mainText": "<p>I am a specialist in working with talent. It is fascinating to work with people who genuinely have passion for the product or the service they design and construct.</p> <p>As a person I am passionate about learning and finding out more along with a need to make a difference - through an entrepreneurial mind set and daring to be unconventional. I genuinely believe in everyone’s ability to do their best, it is a matter of mind set.</p> <p>Lucky me! Surrounded by passionate and by skilled individuals who thrive from complex challenges, and solving them with alike. We share the same values in which I find guidance and inspiration.</p>  ",
