        "orgUnit": "/Employees",
        "mainText": "<p>My main source of motivation has always been my colleagues. To be surrounded by and work with other motivated and creative people inspires me to go the extra mile and succeed as a team.</p><p>You will often find me in a project manager or analytical role as I like to organize the right efforts towards the end goal. I am also interested in creating efficient teams and I have grown fond of the agile methodology.</p><p>Outside of work I prefer to spend my time outdoors with friends and family. I love skiing, hiking and water sports but more often than not, you will find me cooking, playing board games, squash or watching some new tv show.</p> ",
