        "phoneNumber": "+46708303242",
        "office": "Lund",
        "manager": "aleksi.pohjolainen@tretton37.com",
        "orgUnit": "/Employees",
        "mainText": "<p>What led you to this moment? With more than 20 years in the IT-business I’ve created a passion for developing people.</p><p>I feel that the people are our soul, and It's my passion to create a dynamic environment for them to develop their passion. Every single day, I strive to be a better person and try hard to start each day with a smile - even though some days are harder than others!</p><p>Away from work I have three fantastic kids to take care of. I still, occasionally, play some computer games if there is enough time. I enjoy to poke around in the garden, go biking or just ride my Vespa. A nice old fashioned walk always does the trick as well.</p>  ",
