        "mainText": "I’ve been a Java developer for 20 odd years, and live in Ängelholm, Skåne, Sweden.Although Java is my main language- and unix environments my preferred platform - I’m very interested in learning new things and have dabbled among other things with both web frontend (Angular/Typescript) as well as some iOS/Swift. Most recently I’ve started learning Kotlin and hope to be able to use it in my work some day. When I’m not coding or looking into new languages, tools or frameworks I spend my time with my kids (as much as they let me anyway), reading, cooking, listening to music or podcasts or playing the saxophone. ",
