        "orgUnit": "/Employees",
        "mainText": "<p>I discovered my passion for programming and technology when I was a teenager, and since then have been continuously striving to learn new things and to develop.</p><p>I love to surround myself with people who share my interests, and that I can learn from whilst sharing my knowledge with them.</p><p>The thing that drives me the most to develop is the amount of ideas and challenges I encounter every day while solving new problems. There is always a new opportunity to learn. That feeling motivates me to work and create - regardless of whether it is day or night </p><p>However, I have my personal life too and I am happy to spend my free time with my family and friends. I also love travelling and enjoy getting busy with my self built 3D printer and electronic circuits. </p>  ",
