        "mainText": "<p>I still remember the first time I wrote a program using Basic. It was my first try with programming, and I was hooked for life. I enjoy understanding how things work and finding solutions to problems.</p><p>Debugging and performance optimisation is my poison. I am a java developer and I equally enjoy playing with servers, setting up applications, and trying my hands on AWS. </p><p>In my free time, I can be found catching up with some series or a good movie. I also enjoy listening to music and reading books.​</p> ",
