        "orgUnit": "/Employees",
        "mainText": "<p>I have developed solutions with .NET since 2003. Sometimes I have done new things every month, sometimes I have done exactly the same things for five years.</p><p>Whether building production systems for manufacturing, administrative systems for finance, integrations for transport or business intelligence for the public sector, my primary goals are to always find ways to improve and, of course, to make the users happy.</p><p>As well as enjoying when I have actually improved something, I also also like every little victory in the Sisyphean struggle against complexity. Working in a team where everyone learns from each other and shares their knowledge is also a great feeling.</p><p>Outside work, in my youth, I had passions for floorball, gaming and comics. Nowadays, I find that what I enjoy the most is our cottage in Blekinge where I spend a lot of my time.</p> ",
