        "mainText": "<p>I have always been interested in people; to understand and get to know people with different backgrounds and stories. This is one of many reasons why I ended up working with sales and business relations.</p><p>When I'm not working I like to play a few different sports and I also like to cook, but my real passion is travelling. I was born in Stockholm where I have lived most of my life, but I have also lived in Austria and South Africa. My dream is to one day head out on an expedition to the South Pole!</p> ",
