        "orgUnit": "/Employees",
        "mainText": "Strategy and empathy are my strengths and passions. I love being part of a group with intelligent people and solving problems together. As a Scrum Master and proponent of Scrum, I always strive for incremental improvement. This enhancement can be anything from improving a team, making better ramen, or - why not - just to be a happier person.In my spare time, I focus a lot on strength training, cold baths, saunas, making and eating food, and walking around in nature. ",
