        "mainText": "<p>My name is Johannes. I am 30 years old and I live in Malmö with my girlfriend. I have worked as a consultant since I graduated from engineering mathematics at LTH 4 years ago.</p><p>Outside of work I enjoy playing board games, preferably complex strategy games. I also enjoy the outdoors, both shorter trips in Skåne and longer hikes in the Swedish mountains. </p> ",
