        "phoneNumber": "+46736849634",
        "office": "Stockholm",
        "manager": "anders.iggsten@tretton37.com",
        "orgUnit": "/Employees",
        "mainText": "<p>My first addiction in life was guitars - I blame Marty McFly. He introduced me to great artists like Chuck Berry and Van Halen. So when internet started to be a thing, I noticed that bands needed websites, and this triggered a new interest for me. Eventually my guitar addiction got replaced by my new found love of computers (although I still love my guitar and play it whenever I get the chance).</p><p>I like to work with the full-stack, and I love that feeling when I get into the 'zone' and completely lose track of time. That's like music for me.</p><p>I'm a very curious person, and when I'm not on my computer, I love hanging out with my family and friends.</p> ",
