        "orgUnit": "/Employees",
        "mainText": "<p>I'm a driven IT professional who strives to improve no matter what the task or the challenge is; whether building an application, writing a specification or drawing on the whiteboard.</p><p>Solving problems creatively and making work or life easier for others is what I love the most. </p><p>I perform best by working with other people, where knowledge sharing and team spirit provide the building blocks for greatness. Working with me, you'll inevitably get to learn obscure music trivia, the science of storytelling and which horror movie has the best villain. Things that really have little bearing on work, but that make life good.</p> ",
