        "mainText": "<p>I’m driven by challenges with a technical focus on web solutions. My goal is to create business values for my clients and deliver high quality results.</p><p>People usually recognize me by my clothing as I like to stick to pink or purple. Before I got into the world of software development, I was a young rock star in a band called “The Playboyz”.</p> ",
