        "orgUnit": "/Employees",
        "mainText": "<p>25 years ago my father brought home our first computer, and I haven't missed a day since.</p><p>Nowadays I'm even paid to sit by a computer all day!</p><p>When I'm not at the computer, either working or playing video games, I'm probably caring for my plants, or planning the next trip.</p><p>The goal is to visit every country and dive every dive spot.</p> ",
