        "manager": "christof.lindmark@tretton37.com",
        "orgUnit": "/Employees",
        "mainText": "<p>I wrote my first code when I was 7 and instantly fell in love with how empowering it feels. In my career I have completed many different types of programming, but have spent most time on web development. Outside of work I enjoy learning new things and programming phones or other small devices. I have also recently gotten into functional programming.</p><p>Besides coding, I like activities involving high speed and altitude. I love paragliding and falling out of planes! In general I’m interested in everything that flies and I’m planning to start flying sailplanes soon. A couple of years ago I also discovered that I really enjoy alpine skiing and I’m getting better at it every year!</p>          ",
