        "mainText": "<p>I am a front end developer who believes in usability and simplifying your life as a user. If I can make your work more effective and give you a premium feel, whilst at the same time using my code and expertise then I’ve succeeded in my goal.</p><p>I started developing at 11 when my father first showed me different coding languages, and ever since that day I’ve been hooked.</p><p>I am in a constant state of improvement, always striving to learn new things. Knowledge is key, and as a developer you have life long homework ahead of you learning your craft.</p><p>I also love makeup, being sassy and mojitos.</p> ",
