        "mainText": "<p>I am a software developer, a coach, and a consultant with a passion for technology and craftsmanship.</p><p>My desire to learn and share keeps me on the lookout for new and better ways to deliver working software, and I still considering myself a student of the software craft despite being in the business for more than 10 years. </p><p>Usually I am analytical, calm and reasonable, except when it comes to my own kids.</p> ",
