        "mainText": "<p>I love the fact that working with recruitment allows me to meet and interact with a lot of exciting people with different kinds of backgrounds. Finding skilled developers that also share the same values isn’t easy peasy, but that’s why it makes it even more fun. To literally change people’s lives, and helping them to explore their potential is extremely rewarding and I get to do it every day!</p><p>When I'm not hunting skilled developers you will probably find me somewhere in my garden struggling with my peonies or playing with my 2 year old son, Alfred. I also like to play golf and I often brag about my hole-in-one (it was complete luck - but don't tell anyone!)</p> ",
