        "orgUnit": "/Employees",
        "mainText": "<p>''Just a balkan soul with the love for Swedish cold. Having an OG computermaster father, I was always surrounded with technology and computers during my youth. Ever since I got my first Gameboy at the age of 6, I loved pixels.</p><p>For the past couple of years I had the opportunity to get to know a bit of IT business from the inside. Since then, I merged my enabling nature with my passion for organisation to become the person, that makes it possible for everyone else to make it possible.</p><p>In my free time, I like to stroke piano buttons, watch a good TV series or play a board game. My dogs would resent me, if I didn't mention them: Sindi &amp; Neli - woof.''</p>     ",
