        "orgUnit": "/Employees",
        "mainText": "<p>​I’m originally from Norrköping, but moved to Helsingborg in 2012 and have been there ever since! I love the city, and I have found my place! </p><p>I have a passion for​ development, both personally and in my work, and I love taking on new challenges. In my previous roles, I've worked with service and events and it’s something that I’m passionate about. I really enjoy being here at tretton37 as part of the Business Support team! </p><p>In my spare time I do a lot of training; mostly floorball - I play in FC ​​​​Helsingborg in Division 1- but I also like to spend time in the gym or outside running. I have always had sports and training as my number one interest and I have played football and floorball for as long as I can remember. As much as I love to practice sports, I like to watch sports almost even more!​</p> ",
