        "mainText": "I'm an experienced front-end developer with a knack for design, and I can effectively bridge the gap between these two disciplines in every project. With more than 3 years of experience working in different environments, I can quickly adapt to new situations. I take my work seriously and I always make sure to deliver to the best of my abilities.When I'm not in front of a computer screen, I usually sit in front of another screen; perhaps a TV, or maybe a phone.I like travelling, trying new recipes and pretending to have hobbies that aren't related to technology. ",
