        "mainText": "<p>During my time as consultant, I have worked on projects at both large and small companies, which has given me a lot of useful experience. I want to expand my areas of knowledge whenever possible and keep up with new things in the industry.</p><p>I like sharing knowledge with others and I like to work in agile teams. My goal is to accomplish high quality .NET solutions delightfully and effectively using good architecture.</p><p>In my spare time, I like to spend time with my wife and daughter. I also like hiking in the Swedish mountains.</p> ",
