        "orgUnit": "/Admins",
        "mainText": "<p>Interested in all things related to technology, I was bound to end up working and living with geeks. Appreciation for the development and proceedings in life makes me admire them even more.</p><p>Working in different environments from retail to marketing gave me learning opportunities I can now leverage at everyday life and work.</p><p>Trying to keep on top of pop culture with reading (hey, nightstand is not perfect without a book and one or two e-readers), movies and music so I can be ranking higher on pop quizzes.</p><p>Weekends are also a time to test out new recipes and to find new culinary adventures.”</p> ",
